            <br />
            <br />
            <br />
            <p><strong>8 October 2012<br />
            <a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b006qk11" target="_blank">The Moral Maze</a><br />
             BBC Radio 4<br />20.00</strong><br /><br />
             With Melanie Phillips, Claire Fox, Giles Fraser and myself.</p>
             <br />
