            <p><strong>17 October 2012<br />
            <a href="http://asiahouse.org/exhibitions-and-events/detail?id=172" target="_blank">Inside the mind of the Taliban</a><br />
             Asia House<br />63 New Cavendish Street<br />London W1G 7LP <br />18.45</strong><br /><br />
             I am chairing a disciscussion with Alex Strick van Linschoten, editor of <a href="reviews/taliban_poetry.html"><em>Poetry of the Taliban</em></a> and Jason Elliot, author of <em>An Unexpected Light - Travels in Afghanistan and Mirror of the Unseen</em>. Details and tickets from <a href="http://asiahouse.org/exhibitions-and-events/detail?id=172" target="_blank">Asia House</a>.</p>
