            <p><strong>25-26 October 2012<br />
            <a href="http://artsfreedom.org/?page_id=9" target="_blank">All that is banned is desired</a><br />
             The Opera House<br />Oslo<br />Norway</strong><br /><br />
             A conference on artistic freedom of expression. I am chairing a disciscussion on 'Religion and Censorship' with Svetlana Mintcheva, Azhar Usman and Gurpreet Kaur Bhatti. Details and registration <a href="http://artsfreedom.org/?page_id=9" target="_blank">here</a>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
