<TITLE>WashingtonPost.com: Demonic Males: Apes and the Origins of Human Violence</TITLE>

<!-- ********** THE DOCUMENT TITLE ENDS HERE ***** -->

</HEAD>
<BODY bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
