      style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:Papyrus'>Local physiological
      adaptation and the energetic costs of alternative morphs in the soapberry
      bug, <span class=SpellE><i>Jadera</i></span><i> <span class=SpellE>haematoloma</span></i>
      (Hemiptera)</span></strong><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span
      style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:Papyrus'>. Respirometric studies of
      different populations across </span></b><st1:place><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:
