    <TD VALIGN="top" width="318"> 
      <p class="Title"> Memetics UK</p>
      <p> <font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">
          This site, which began with the Bristol based <a href="memelab.htm">memelab</a>,
          can also be accessed through www.memetics.com.</font></p>
      <p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">I hope to provide a simple,
      but useful, resource for finding out what is happening in the world of
      memes and memetics.</font></p>
