  &quot;Oh, you're the fellow who pinched my title!&quot; It was not a week
  after the advance information for my book <em>Virus of the Mind</em> was sent
  to <em>Books in Print</em> that I walked into Barnes &amp; Noble and saw his
  essay featured on the cover of <em>Free Inquiry</em> magazine. Well, I
  suppose the meme infected both of us at about the same time...</p>
  </td>
