  <p class=MsoNormal>Here's a smart young man that I'm a big fan of. He's
  written quite a bit about the future of humanity, especially the
  &quot;singularity&quot; predicted when artificial intelligence overtakes
  human intelligence. He's worth getting to know.</p>
  </td>
